I'm back for sure this time but I'm out of place in the posts so just suffer 
along with me until I get caught up, ok?

* Iron passed through the halls of the Maximal City, leading the followers 
towards the holo room where she was going to pick up the pace a bit. But 
Hell Drak's attitude needed to change if she was going to stay 
alive...mainly around her.
IR didn't like people that acted like that, like a snob.
But she would say nothing.
Just about to the holo rooms IR was stopped by Cheetor and Depth Charge.
She blinked.*

" Rooms? Well, if you want quarters then just pick which ever ones you want 
that aren't already taken."

* She gestured towards the training rooms though.*

" But you guys should be in there with the rest."
